Package starwars

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SWActionInterface
    Interface that allows SWAction and SWAffordance to have a common ancestor (and thus be stored in the same structures) despite one extending Action and the other extending Affordance.
    SWEntityInterface
    All Entities and Actors in the starwars client package should implement this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    Driver class for the Star Wars package with GridController.
    SWAction
    Base class for all intransitive commands/Actions in the starwars world.
    SWActor  
    SWAffordance
    Class that represents Affordances in the starwars world.
    SWEntity
    Class that represents inanimate objects in the Star Wars world.
    SWGrid
    Grid of SWLocations.
    SWLegend
    This class represents "legends" - major characters - in the Star Wars universe.
    SWLocation
    Class that models locations in Star Wars.
    SWLocation.SWLocationMaker
    Factory class used by Grids to instantiate SWLocations
    SWRobots
    This class represents "droids" in the Star Wars universe.
    SWWorld
    Class representing a world in the Star Wars universe.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Capability
    Capabilities that various entities may have.
    Team
    Enumerator class for different types of Teams for the SWActors.
